summary: A ring with a waterwalking enchantment on it.
descriptionHtml:
Adds a ring with a waterwalking enchantment to two leveled item lists. Both in enchanted item lists. One list is the normal item list, the other is the expert list. I\'ve done this so to increase the chance of getting a ring later on in the game. This means everyone with access to these lists has a chance to get this ring. Merchants, chests and npc\'s might have it.

If you\'re not a patient person, i also added a ring on the edge of the well in Riften.
author: EzDC
